Repeat, backup.

57:44.028 --> 57:46.230
Where are you
taking the money?

57:46.230 --> 57:47.364
To the truck stop.

57:47.364 --> 57:48.699
Where? Exactly. Where?

57:48.699 --> 57:51.502
On the main highway,
the Texaco.

57:55.205 --> 57:57.675
Son of a bitch!

57:57.675 --> 57:59.276
Officer! Officer,
you gotta help me!

57:59.276 --> 58:00.377
My wife's
been kidnapped.

58:00.377 --> 58:02.179
Drop the gun!
Whoa, wait.

58:02.179 --> 58:03.280
Get down!

58:03.280 --> 58:04.615
I know where she is.

58:04.615 --> 58:06.951
Get down on the
ground! Do it!

58:06.951 --> 58:10.087
All right, I'm down.
Listen to me. He's in on it.

58:10.087 --> 58:12.289
He's with the trucker.
They kidnapped my wife.

58:12.289 --> 58:14.358
There's 4 of them.
They all work together.

58:14.358 --> 58:16.026
They got her right now
at a truck stop, the Texaco--

58:16.026 --> 58:20.731
Face down! Shut up!
You in the pickup,
you all right?

58:20.731 --> 58:22.199
