got to believe me.

58:22.199 --> 58:23.568
Can you hear me?
Why else would
I be out here?

58:23.568 --> 58:25.202
Yes, sir. I'm OK.

58:25.202 --> 58:26.671
Can you get out?
Help me, goddamn it.

58:26.671 --> 58:28.138
Yes, I can.
Please don't shoot me.

58:28.138 --> 58:29.874
Look in the cab.
There's a bag with money,

58:29.874 --> 58:31.508
and I swear to god,
it's right in there.

58:31.508 --> 58:34.211
Face down, spread-eagle,
and shut up!

58:35.713 --> 58:37.414
Get out, damn it!
We have to get
to the truck stop.

58:37.414 --> 58:40.117
Goddamn it, listen to what
I'm telling you!

58:40.117 --> 58:41.552
Shut the fuck up!

58:41.552 --> 58:42.920
Unh!

58:52.462 --> 58:54.364
Hey, shit for brains.

58:54.364 --> 58:56.000
Ha ha ha.

58:56.000 --> 58:58.002
( gunshot )

59:17.321 --> 59:19.590
Shots fired.

59:20.591 --> 59:22.693
Officer down.

59:27.331 --> 59:29.266
Suspect identified.

59:32.002 --> 59:34.739
