59:48.418 --> 59:51.121
Sheriff, hang on.
We're getting you
an ambulance.

59:54.091 --> 59:56.593
All units, all units,
officer down--

59:56.593 --> 59:58.963
Repeat, officer down.

01:01:18.242 --> 01:01:19.744
Look, I don't know,
damn it.

01:01:19.744 --> 01:01:22.079
He was supposed to be here
a half an hour ago,

01:01:22.079 --> 01:01:25.750
and I heard a report
on the police band
about a cop down.

01:01:25.750 --> 01:01:28.418
I'm leaving. I can't--
There's too much
heat around here.

01:01:28.418 --> 01:01:29.920
So stay off
the airwaves,

01:01:29.920 --> 01:01:32.322
get his wife, and
meet me at the barn.

01:01:32.322 --> 01:01:34.792
I don't care if we
have to drive all night.

01:05:27.357 --> 01:05:29.059
( horn honks )

01:05:35.165 --> 01:05:36.733
Daddy, you're home!

01:05:36.733 --> 01:05:38.568
Hey, Deke.
Miss me?

01:05:38.568 --> 01:05:39.569
Yeah.

01:05:39.569 --> 01:05:40.770
Deke, get back to bed.

01:05:40.770 --> 01:05:43.340
Warren, I thought
you were coming back
next week.

01:05:43.340 --> 01:05:46.376
Yeah. Well,
I finished early,
and now I'm home.

01:05:46.376 --> 01:05:48.512
Al and Billy are
coming over in
a little while, too.

01:05:48.512 --> 01:05:51.448
